\pard\sa200\sl276\slmult1\f0\fs22\lang9 1. Nghi\f1\lang1066\u7879?p v\u7909? ch\u7845?m c\f0\lang1033\'f4ng\par
Nghi\f1\lang1066\u7879?p v\u7909? ch\u7845?m c\f0\lang1033\'f4ng c\'f3 s\f1\lang1066\u7921? kh\f0\lang1033\'e1c bi\f1\lang1066\u7879?t gi\u7919?a hai m\f0\lang1033\'f4 h\'ecnh nghi\f1\lang1066\u7879?p v\u7909? ph\f0\lang1033\'e2n ca \f2\endash  ch\f1\lang1066\u7845?m c\f0\lang1033\'f4ng ph\f1\lang1066\u7893? bi\u7871?n hi\u7879?n nay:\par
\par
Nghi\u7879?p v\u7909? ch\u7845?m c\f0\lang1033\'f4ng ca h\'e0nh ch\'ednh:\par
\par
Nh\'e2n vi\'ean l\'e0m gi\f1\lang1066\u7901? h\f0\lang1033\'e0nh ch\'ednh, th\f1\lang1066\u7881?nh tho\u7843?ng l\f0\lang1033\'e0m th\'eam gi\f1\lang1066\u7901?.\par
Th\f3\u432?\f1\u7901?ng g\u7863?p \u7903? b\u7897? ph\u7853?n v\f3\'e3n ph\f0\lang1033\'f2ng c\f1\lang1066\u7911?a t\u7845?t c\u7843? c\f0\lang1033\'e1c \f3\'f0\u417?n v\f1\lang1066\u7883?.\par
Nghi\u7879?p v\u7909? ch\u7845?m c\f0\lang1033\'f4ng ca k\'edp lu\'e2n phi\'ean:\par
\par
Nh\'e2n vi\'ean l\'e0m vi\f1\lang1066\u7879?c theo ca k\f0\lang1033\'edp v\'e0 c\'f3 \f3\'f0\f1\lang1066\u7893?i ca\par
Th\f3\u432?\f1\u7901?ng g\u7863?p \u7903? b\u7897? ph\u7853?n s\u7843?n xu\u7845?t c\f0\lang1033\'f4ng ty s\f1\lang1066\u7843?n xu\u7845?t may m\u7863?c, \f3\'f0i\f1\u7879?n t\u7917?, nh\f0\lang1033\'e2n vi\'ean ph\f1\lang1066\u7909?c v\u7909? nh\f0\lang1033\'e0 h\'e0ng, c\f1\lang1066\u7917?a h\f0\lang1033\'e0ng b\'e1n l\f1\lang1066\u7867?, r\u7841?p chi\u7871?u phim,\'85\par
Ngo\f0\lang1033\'e0i ra, c\'f2n m\f1\lang1066\u7897?t m\f0\lang1033\'f4 h\'ecnh ch\f1\lang1066\u7845?m c\f0\lang1033\'f4ng \f3\'f0ang ph\f0\'e1t tri\f1\lang1066\u7875?n kh\f0\lang1033\'e1c l\'e0 ch\f1\lang1066\u7845?m c\f0\lang1033\'f4ng theo gi\f1\lang1066\u7901? linh ho\u7841?t:\par
\par
Nh\f0\lang1033\'e2n vi\'ean l\'e0m vi\f1\lang1066\u7879?c linh \f3\'f0\f1\u7897?ng, kh\f0\lang1033\'f4ng c\f1\lang1066\u7847?n theo khung gi\u7901? c\u7889? \f3\'f0\f1\u7883?nh\par
Th\f3\u432?\f1\u7901?ng g\u7863?p \u7903? nh\f0\lang1033\'e2n vi\'ean d\f1\lang1066\u7883?ch v\u7909? s\u7917?a ch\u7919?a m\f0\lang1033\'e1y t\'ednh, nh\'e2n vi\'ean ph\f1\lang1066\u7909?c v\u7909? nh\f0\lang1033\'e0 h\'e0ng, r\f1\lang1066\u7841?p chi\u7871?u phim, \'85\par
B\u7843?ng ch\u7845?m c\f0\lang1033\'f4ng h\'e0ng ng\'e0y/h\'e0ng th\'e1ng \f3\'f0\u432?\f1\lang1066\u7907?c l\u7853?p d\u7921?a tr\f0\lang1033\'ean c\'e1c y\f1\lang1066\u7871?u t\u7889? sau:\par
\par
\f2\endash  Th\f1\u7901?i gian ng\f3\u432?\f1\u7901?i lao \f3\'f0\f1\u7897?ng c\f0\lang1033\'f3 \f3\'f0i l\f0\'e0m: \f3\'f0\u432?\f1\lang1066\u7907?c ghi nh\u7853?n th\u7911? c\f0\lang1033\'f4ng ho\f1\lang1066\u7863?c b\u7857?ng thi\u7871?t b\u7883? ch\u7845?m c\f0\lang1033\'f4ng, d\f1\lang1066\u7921?a tr\f0\lang1033\'ean quy \f3\'f0\f1\lang1066\u7883?nh ph\f0\lang1033\'e2n ca, quy \f3\'f0\f1\lang1066\u7883?nh l\f0\lang1033\'e0m th\'eam, \f3\'f0i mu\f1\lang1066\u7897?n v\u7873? s\u7899?m,\'85\par
\par
\f2\endash  Th\f1\u7901?i gian ng\f3\u432?\f1\u7901?i lao \f3\'f0\f1\u7897?ng v\u7855?ng m\u7863?t, bao g\u7891?m:\par
\par
\f3\'d0i c\f0\lang1033\'f4ng t\'e1c: \f3\'d0\u432?\f1\lang1066\u7907?c ghi nh\u7853?n b\u7857?ng \f3\'f0\u417?n c\f0\lang1033\'f4ng t\'e1c.\par
Ngh\f1\lang1066\u7881? ph\f0\lang1033\'e9p/ngh\f1\lang1066\u7881? thai s\u7843?n/ngh\u7881? \u7889?m: \f3\'d0\u432?\f1\u7907?c ghi nh\u7853?n b\u7857?ng \f3\'f0\u417?n xin ngh\f1\u7881? ho\u7863?c kh\f0\lang1033\'f4ng c\'f3 th\'f4ng tin \f3\'f0i l\f0\'e0m th\'ec x\'e1c \f3\'f0\f1\lang1066\u7883?nh l\f0\lang1033\'e0 ngh\f1\lang1066\u7881?.\par
Ngh\u7881? l\u7877? t\u7871?t: Theo quy \f3\'f0\f1\u7883?nh c\u7911?a nh\f0\lang1033\'e0 n\f3\u432?\f1\lang1066\u7899?c v\f0\lang1033\'e0 doanh nghi\f1\lang1066\u7879?p.\par
