M\'f4 h\'ecnh ch\f1\lang1066\u7845?m c\f0\lang1033\'f4ng h\'e0nh ch\'ednh\par
Lu\f1\lang1066\u7891?ng nghi\u7879?p v\u7909? ch\u7845?m c\f0\lang1033\'f4ng h\'e0nh ch\'ednh xu\f1\lang1066\u7845?t ph\f0\lang1033\'e1t t\f1\lang1066\u7915? vi\u7879?c HR x\f0\lang1033\'e2y d\f1\lang1066\u7921?ng quy \f3\'f0\f1\u7883?nh ch\u7845?m c\f0\lang1033\'f4ng cho to\'e0n h\f1\lang1066\u7879? th\u7889?ng c\f0\lang1033\'f4ng ty. Sau khi ph\f1\lang1066\u7893? bi\u7871?n cho nh\f0\lang1033\'e2n vi\'ean v\'e0 th\f1\lang1066\u7921?c hi\u7879?n ch\u7845?m c\f0\lang1033\'f4ng chi ti\f1\lang1066\u7871?t h\f0\lang1033\'e0ng ng\'e0y, HR s\f1\lang1066\u7869? t\u7893?ng h\u7907?p c\f0\lang1033\'f4ng. B\'e1o c\'e1o t\f1\lang1066\u7893?ng h\u7907?p c\f0\lang1033\'f4ng c\f1\lang1066\u7911?a t\u7915?ng c\f0\lang1033\'e1 nh\'e2n s\f1\lang1066\u7869? \f3\'f0\u432?\f1\u7907?c g\u7917?i cho nh\f0\lang1033\'e2n vi\'ean. Sau khi c\'f3 x\'e1c nh\f1\lang1066\u7853?n c\u7911?a nh\f0\lang1033\'e2n vi\'ean, HR s\f1\lang1066\u7869? th\u7921?c hi\u7879?n b\f0\lang1033\'e1o c\'e1o c\'f4ng \f3\'f0\f1\lang1066\u7875? t\f0\lang1033\'ednh l\f3\u432?\u417?ng v\f0\'e0 thanh to\'e1n cho ng\f3\u432?\f1\lang1066\u7901?i lao \f3\'f0\f1\u7897?ng.\par
\par
N\u7871?u c\f0\lang1033\'f3 b\f1\lang1066\u7845?t c\u7913? ph\f0\lang1033\'e1t sinh n\'e0o trong qu\'e1 tr\'ecnh c\'f4ng t\'e1c: xin ngh\f1\lang1066\u7881?, \f3\'f0i c\f0\lang1033\'f4ng t\'e1c, ngh\f1\lang1066\u7881? ph\f0\lang1033\'e9p,\'85 Qu\f1\lang1066\u7843?n l\f0\lang1033\'fd s\f1\lang1066\u7869? duy\u7879?t \f3\'f0\u417?n\par
\par
1.1.1. Nghi\f1\u7879?p v\u7909? ch\u7845?m c\f0\lang1033\'f4ng h\'e0ng ng\'e0y\par
\f3\'d0\f1\lang1066\u7889?i v\u7899?i nh\f0\lang1033\'e2n vi\'ean HR: H\'e0ng ng\'e0y, HR th\f1\lang1066\u7921?c hi\u7879?n ch\u7845?m c\f0\lang1033\'f4ng chi ti\f1\lang1066\u7871?t v\f0\lang1033\'e0 theo d\'f5i nh\'e2n vi\'ean ngh\f1\lang1066\u7881?, nh\f0\lang1033\'e2n vi\'ean \f3\'f0i mu\f1\lang1066\u7897?n, v\u7873? s\u7899?m,\'85c\f3\'e3n c\f1\u7913? v\f0\lang1033\'e0o d\f1\lang1066\u7919? li\u7879?u ch\u7845?m c\f0\lang1033\'f4ng v\'e0 c\'e1c \f3\'f0\u417?n xin ngh\f1\lang1066\u7881?, \f3\'f0i c\f0\lang1033\'f4ng t\'e1c, l\'e0m th\'eam gi\f1\lang1066\u7901? (n\u7871?u c\f0\lang1033\'f3),\'85\par
\par
\f3\'d0\f1\lang1066\u7889?i v\u7899?i nh\f0\lang1033\'e2n vi\'ean:\par
\par
H\'e0ng ng\'e0y nh\'e2n vi\'ean th\f1\lang1066\u7921?c hi\u7879?n ch\u7845?m c\f0\lang1033\'f4ng th\'f4ng qua c\'f4ng c\f1\lang1066\u7909? ch\u7845?m c\f0\lang1033\'f4ng.\par
N\f1\lang1066\u7871?u ngh\u7881? ho\u7863?c \f3\'f0i c\f0\lang1033\'f4ng t\'e1c th\'ec th\f1\lang1066\u7921?c hi\u7879?n l\u7853?p \f3\'f0\u417?n xin ngh\f1\u7881?/ \f3\'f0i c\f0\lang1033\'f4ng t\'e1c \f3\'f0\f1\lang1066\u7875? \f3\'f0\u432?\f1\u7907?c ch\u7845?m c\f0\lang1033\'f4ng.\par
N\f1\lang1066\u7871?u c\f0\lang1033\'f3 l\'e0m th\'eam gi\f1\lang1066\u7901? th\f0\lang1033\'ec c\f3\u361?ng c\f1\lang1066\u7847?n l\u7853?p \f3\'f0\u417?n \'f0\f1\u7873? ngh\u7883? l\f0\lang1033\'e0m th\'eam gi\f1\lang1066\u7901? \f3\'f0\f1\u7875? \f3\'f0\u432?\f1\u7907?c ch\u7845?m c\f0\lang1033\'f4ng t\f3\'e3ng ca.\par
\'d0\f1\lang1066\u7889?i v\u7899?i qu\u7843?n l\f0\lang1033\'fd: Duy\f1\lang1066\u7879?t \f3\'f0\u417?n xin ngh\f1\u7881?, \f3\'f0\u417?n \'f0i c\f0\lang1033\'f4ng t\'e1c v\'e0 \f3\'f0\f1\lang1066\u7873? ngh\u7883? l\f0\lang1033\'e0m th\'eam cho nh\'e2n vi\'ean theo quy \f3\'f0\f1\lang1066\u7883?nh.\par
\par
1.1.2. Nghi\u7879?p v\u7909? ch\u7845?m c\f0\lang1033\'f4ng cu\f1\lang1066\u7889?i th\f0\lang1033\'e1ng\par
\f3\'d0\f1\lang1066\u7889?i v\u7899?i HR:\par
\par
T\u7893?ng h\u7907?p c\f0\lang1033\'f4ng theo ng\'e0y c\'f4ng cho nh\'e2n vi\'ean: ph\'e2n bi\f1\lang1066\u7879?t c\f0\lang1033\'f4ng ng\'e0y th\f3\u432?\f1\lang1066\u7901?ng, ng\f0\lang1033\'e0y ngh\f1\lang1066\u7881?, ng\f0\lang1033\'e0y l\f1\lang1066\u7877? v\f0\lang1033\'e0 l\'e0m th\'eam gi\f1\lang1066\u7901? ban ng\f0\lang1033\'e0y, ban \f3\'f0\f0\'eam theo quy \f3\'f0\f1\lang1066\u7883?nh nh\f0\lang1033\'e0 n\f3\u432?\f1\lang1066\u7899?c.\par
X\f0\lang1033\'e1c nh\f1\lang1066\u7853?n c\f0\lang1033\'f4ng v\f1\lang1066\u7899?i nh\f0\lang1033\'e2n vi\'ean.\par
\f3\'d0\f1\lang1066\u7889?i v\u7899?i nh\f0\lang1033\'e2n vi\'ean: X\'e1c nh\f1\lang1066\u7853?n c\f0\lang1033\'f4ng.\par
\par
1.1.3. Nghi\f1\lang1066\u7879?p v\u7909? ch\u7845?m c\f0\lang1033\'f4ng ph\'e1t sinh\par
\f3\'d0\f1\lang1066\u7889?i v\u7899?i HR:\par
\par
Tr\f3\u432?\f1\u7901?ng h\u7907?p ngh\u7881? l\u7877? HR t\u7921? ch\u7845?m c\f0\lang1033\'f4ng cho nh\'e2n vi\'ean theo quy \f3\'f0\f1\lang1066\u7883?nh.\par
HR theo d\f0\lang1033\'f5i t\'ecnh h\'ecnh ngh\f1\lang1066\u7881? ph\f0\lang1033\'e9p c\f1\lang1066\u7911?a nh\f0\lang1033\'e2n vi\'ean \f3\'f0\f1\lang1066\u7875? ki\u7875?m tra vi\u7879?c duy\u7879?t \f3\'f0\u417?n ho\f1\u7863?c thanh to\f0\lang1033\'e1n ph\'e9p t\f1\lang1066\u7891?n b\u7857?ng ti\u7873?n.\par
HR b\f0\lang1033\'e1o c\'e1o ch\f1\lang1066\u7845?m c\f0\lang1033\'f4ng v\f1\lang1066\u7899?i l\f0\lang1033\'e3nh \f3\'f0\f1\lang1066\u7841?o \f3\'f0\f1\u7883?nh k\u7923? ho\u7863?c khi c\f0\lang1033\'f3 y\'eau c\f1\lang1066\u7847?u.\par
\f3\'d0\f1\u7889?i v\u7899?i nh\f0\lang1033\'e2n vi\'ean: Tr\f3\u432?\f1\lang1066\u7901?ng h\u7907?p ngh\u7881? l\u7877? nh\f0\lang1033\'e2n vi\'ean kh\'f4ng c\f1\lang1066\u7847?n ch\u7845?m c\f0\lang1033\'f4ng ho\f1\lang1066\u7863?c l\f0\lang1033\'e0m \f3\'f0\u417?n.\par
