Lu\f1\lang1066\u7891?ng nghi\u7879?p v\u7909? ch\u7845?m c\f0\lang1033\'f4ng theo ca c\f3\u361?ng xu\f1\lang1066\u7845?t ph\f0\lang1033\'e1t t\f1\lang1066\u7915? vi\u7879?c x\f0\lang1033\'e2y d\f1\lang1066\u7921?ng quy tr\f0\lang1033\'ecnh ch\f1\lang1066\u7845?m c\f0\lang1033\'f4ng c\f1\lang1066\u7911?a HR. Sau \f3\'f0\f0\lang1033\'f3 vi\f1\lang1066\u7879?c l\u7853?p b\u7843?ng ph\f0\lang1033\'e2n ca s\f1\lang1066\u7869? \f3\'f0\u432?\f1\u7907?c duy\u7879?t l\u7841?i b\u7903?i c\u7845?p qu\u7843?n l\f0\lang1033\'fd. Nh\f1\lang1066\u7919?ng quy tr\f0\lang1033\'ecnh ti\f1\lang1066\u7871?p theo t\f3\u432?\u417?ng t\f1\u7921? nh\f3\u432? lu\f1\u7891?ng nghi\u7879?p v\u7909? ch\u7845?m c\f0\lang1033\'f4ng h\'e0nh ch\'ednh.\par
