1.2.1. Nghi\f1\lang1066\u7879?p v\u7909? ch\u7845?m c\f0\lang1033\'f4ng h\'e0ng ng\'e0y\par
\f3\'d0\f1\lang1066\u7889?i v\u7899?i HR:\par
\par
Theo d\f0\lang1033\'f5i b\f1\lang1066\u7843?ng ph\f0\lang1033\'e2n ca.\par
Theo d\'f5i t\'ecnh h\'ecnh tu\'e2n th\f1\lang1066\u7911? quy \f3\'f0\f1\u7883?nh v\u7873? gi\u7901? gi\u7845?c l\f0\lang1033\'e0m vi\f1\lang1066\u7879?c \f3\'f0\f1\u7875? c\f0\lang1033\'f3 nh\f1\lang1066\u7855?c nh\u7903? ho\u7863?c tr\u7915? l\f3\u432?\u417?ng.\par
HR theo d\f0\lang1033\'f5i ngh\f1\lang1066\u7881? b\f0\lang1033\'f9 \f3\'f0\f1\lang1066\u7875? ki\u7875?m so\f0\lang1033\'e1t vi\f1\lang1066\u7879?c duy\u7879?t \f3\'f0\u417?n ngh\f1\u7881? b\f0\lang1033\'f9 t\f3\u432?\u417?ng t\f1\lang1066\u7921? ngh\u7881? ph\f0\lang1033\'e9p.\par
\f3\'d0\f1\lang1066\u7889?i v\u7899?i nh\f0\lang1033\'e2n vi\'ean:\par
\par
\f3\'d0\f1\lang1066\u7893?i ca cho nhau khi c\f0\lang1033\'f3 vi\f1\lang1066\u7879?c \f3\'f0\f1\u7897?t xu\u7845?t nh\f3\u432?ng kh\f0\lang1033\'f4ng mu\f1\lang1066\u7889?n ngh\u7881? l\f0\lang1033\'e0m.\par
M\f1\lang1066\u7897?t s\u7889? \f3\'f0\u417?n v\f1\u7883? kh\f0\lang1033\'f4ng t\'ednh l\f3\u432?\u417?ng t\'e3ng ca m\f0\'e0 cho ph\'e9p ngh\f1\lang1066\u7881? b\f0\lang1033\'f9 cho th\f1\lang1066\u7901?i gian t\f3\'e3ng ca, khi ngh\f1\u7881? b\f0\lang1033\'f9, nh\'e2n vi\'ean l\f1\lang1066\u7853?p \f3\'f0\u417?n xin ngh\f1\u7881? b\f0\lang1033\'f9 \f3\'f0\f1\lang1066\u7875? v\u7851?n \f3\'f0\u432?\f1\u7907?c h\f3\u432?\f1\u7903?ng l\f3\u432?\u417?ng nh\f1\u7919?ng ng\f0\lang1033\'e0y \f3\'f0\f0\'f3.\par
\f3\'d0\f1\lang1066\u7889?i v\u7899?i qu\u7843?n l\f0\lang1033\'fd: \f3\'d0\f1\lang1066\u7893?i ca \f3\'f0\f1\u7883?nh k\u7923? (hay c\f0\lang1033\'f2n g\f1\lang1066\u7885?i l\f0\lang1033\'e0 x\f1\lang1066\u7871?p ca l\f0\lang1033\'e0m vi\f1\lang1066\u7879?c) cho c\f0\lang1033\'e1c nh\'e2n vi\'ean ho\f1\lang1066\u7863?c c\f0\lang1033\'e1c b\f1\lang1066\u7897? ph\u7853?n \f3\'f0\f1\u7875? \f3\'f0\f1\u7843?m b\u7843?o s\u7913?c kh\u7887?e cho nh\f0\lang1033\'e2n vi\'ean nh\f3\u432?ng v\f1\lang1066\u7851?n \f3\'f0\f1\u7911? nh\f0\lang1033\'e2n s\f1\lang1066\u7921? th\u7921?c hi\u7879?n ho\u7841?t \f3\'f0\f1\u7897?ng s\u7843?n xu\u7845?t kinh doanh.\par
